Install:
--------
1. Download /src dir to local disc
2. Go to chrome://extensions/
3. Click "Load unpacked extensions"
4. Select the src dir you downloaded

Usage:
------
1. Add bookmarks to your bookmark bar
2. Press Meta + <1-9> to access bookmarks #1-9

Problems? E-Mail felix@debuggable.com.

Known Issues
------------
* Currently not available as a packed version, seems like this is broken for Chrome under OSX : /
* Only tested on OSX 10.5 with Chrome 4.0.207.0, let me know if this works on Windows